Hi everyone! I'm Bayram.
I have experience in C, Ruby, RoR, Solidity, also have a good background in Cryptography.
Learning Rust for 3 months. Here are my couple of posts in Rusts:
1) https://medium.com/swlh/strategy-design-pattern-in-rust-5f5486cd294c?source=friends_link&sk=6871f4761dc6c4b7c0bc3ccefd22e408

Hello Bayram! What are you interested in working on?
Hi Joshua! Primary interest is Cryptography + Blockchain. But I also have experience in ML, especially in NLP (training chatbots).

you might be interested in working with @kinnison on rustup verification of the binary downloads:
